<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634110192323276798" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634118483195587834">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Click on <em>CheckBox </em>and Label will indicate <em>Checked </em>state of <em>CheckBox</em>. If the <em>CheckBox </em>is checked, the label contains 'CheckBox is checked!', otherwise, the label contains 'CheckBox is unchecked!'</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>CheckBox </em>contains the <em>Checked </em>property and <em>CheckedChange </em>event for manipulating with checked indicator. The <em>Checked </em>property indicates whether <em>CheckBox </em>is checked. The <em>CheckedChange </em>event invoke when <em>Checked </em>property are changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
